0.1.name: wordpress/myc4-import
0.1.description:
"MYC4 is an online marketplace that connects you directly with African entrepreneurs, who lack capital to develop their businesses" - From MYC4 About page

This plugin gives you the ability to show your blog readers the businesses in which you invested using the MYC4 platform.
